@startuml
title UC-02 View Tracks in Album

|Visitor|
start
:Navigate to Album page (via Albums list or deep link);

|System|
:Resolve albumId and load album context;
if (Album found?) then (yes)
  :Render album header metadata;
  :Fetch tracks for album from RDS;

  |Storage|
  :Return track list result;

  |System|
  if (Tracks available?) then (yes)
    :Render track list with title, duration, track number;
    :Expose shareable URL for the page;

    |Visitor|
    :Review tracks and pick one to preview;
    stop
  else (no)
    :Render empty state message and keep navigation controls;

    |Visitor|
    :Return to Albums or stay on page;
    stop
  endif
else (no)
  :Render 404 Not Found with link back to Albums;

  |Visitor|
  :Navigate back to Albums list;
  stop
endif
@enduml
